{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"37233-piggy-wants-to-fly","title":"Piggy Wants to Fly","description":"As Piggy gazes upon a butterfly happy in flight, Piggy dreams of flying. Can Piggy learn to fly like a butterfly?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Stephanie  Wei"],"illustrators":["Youm Kosal"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/37233-piggy-wants-to-fly"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101348/size3/9590904b7e94f28a5dd15888d0ac5885.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101348/size6/9590904b7e94f28a5dd15888d0ac5885.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70542/size6/47344731bfa3e8085e97de70d35441a4.jpg","text":"\"I want to fly like the butterfly does.\"","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70543/size6/d5c7f6f5dfee9ce3e833eaab7d4acf9f.jpg","text":"\"Follow me!\" said the butterfly.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70544/size6/91ea3065c152c6c495e00a236b4ee7f5.jpg","text":"\"But I do not have wings, I\ncannot fly.\"","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70545/size6/67ad4cca734c3e55d731593e46b42dd9.jpg","text":"\"I know, I’ll\nuse palm leaves to make wings!\"","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70546/size6/31c6741a95c31d740a21307ed2751d51.jpg","text":"\"Flap\nyour wings hard to fly!\" cried the butterfly.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70548/size6/7647ba86cc8a11088e112fedcadcf056.jpg","text":"\"I cannot seem to fly,\" said Piggy. \"Let\nme try one more time.\"","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70549/size6/0341dba2334005d0007363088c3d4237.jpg","text":"\"Look!\nI can fly!\" Piggy said leaping off the branch.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70550/size6/af9e26555944a7cb9f3d760927035c46.jpg","text":"\"Oh\nno! Why did I fall? I do not have wings like you, so I will have to be okay with not flying.\"","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70552/size6/2ada3cdfed5afc779e05cad6356d7516.jpg","text":"10/10","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":9,"words":87}}